name: SHOWER SPACES
description:
Today in the shower I talked and talked and talked outloud as if I was in a Twitter space, the more I tried to talk about my art the more of my dark past came out instead. So I’d try and talk a different way, a different part of my story, about why I paint like I do and where my creativity came from, and it took me back into too much pain, and too much personal information. And by the end of it I felt like I couldn’t talk on Twitter spaces today at all. 

STOREEZ Personal daily art story by Treasvre Trove/ Cat BROWN 
Number 2
